commit.title: [stm] Remove `opacity_guarantee` from the classification.
commit.message:
[stm] Remove `opacity_guarantee` from the classification.

This flag is used to avoid proof delegation, however it is not used
consistently, and it has little to do with opacity on itself.

After #9655 we can instead just test the proof information to see
whether the proof can be delegated or not.
